+        <li><code>log(a+bε)=log a + b/a ε</code> for <code>a&gt;0</code></li>
+        <li><code>sqrt(a+bε)=√a + b/(2√a) ε</code> for <code>a&gt;0</code></li>
+      </ul>
+    </article>
+  </section>
+
